These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, dog, ferret, frog
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, bartender, designer, software-developer
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. the person driving the airplane is the owner of the frog##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the bartender##1
3. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the designer is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the ship is between the software-developer and the owner of the goldfish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Pet         | frog      | goldfish | dog | ferret |
| Job   | designer | security-guard  | bartender   | software-developer    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, hip-hop, country, soul
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, lemonade
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan of country##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the fan of trance is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the fan of soul is between the fan of hip-hop and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Music-Genre   | country     | trance | soul  | hip-hop |
| Beverage     | lemonade        | almond-milk  | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different games are played: canasta, snooker, whist, monopoly
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, trance, punk, pop
1. the german is between the person playing canasta and the person playing monopoly##2
2. the argentine is the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of rock is the person playing whist##1
4. the fan of rock is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the person playing snooker and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | canasta | snooker   | monopoly     | whist     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Music-Genre     | pop      | trance | punk | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, fanta, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, salsa, soul
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, woodworking, board-games, baking
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the fan of soul is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person drinking fanta is the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of salsa is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee  | iced-tea   | fanta     | milk |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul      | pop        | punk     |
| Hobby         | board-games | rock-climbing | baking | woodworking   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different games are played: go, poker, canasta, backgammon
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, blend, dannemann, bongani
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the person playing backgammon is the bongani-smoker##1
2. the person playing canasta is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the bongani-smoker##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the blend-smoker is on the far left##1
7. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
8. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the baccarat-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Game   | go   | backgammon   | canasta | poker |
| Cigar         | blend      | bongani | baccarat      | dannemann |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

