.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, golf, climbing, cricket
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, sudoku, woodworking
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, fonseca, havana, chaman
1. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
2. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Sport    | climbing   | cricket      | golf       | badminton |
| Hobby   | camping | woodworking | sudoku     | fishing |
| Cigar     | chaman     | fonseca  | vegafina | havana |

