.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, parkour, water-polo, weightlifting
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, orange, purple, lavender
1. the person who likes purple is the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who likes orange is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who likes turquise##2
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person who's sport is handball is the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person who likes purple is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | tea          | hot-chocolate | 7up        |
| Sport   | water-polo     | parkour | weightlifting   | handball     |
| Color           | turquise | orange         | lavender         | purple |

