.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
House: gothic-revival, colonial, cottage, victorian
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, librarian, scientist, social-worker
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, roller, van, bike
1. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
2. the scientist is the gothic-revival house##1
3. the social-worker is the cottage house##1
4. the cottage house is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the journalist and the gothic-revival house##2
6. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the scientist##3
7. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4
8. the gothic-revival house is between the colonial house and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| House         | colonial | gothic-revival      | cottage       | victorian    |
| Job           | librarian  | scientist  | social-worker | journalist |
| Transport   | bike      | van | roller         | taxi    |

