.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, ambient, funk, country
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, october, june
1. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the fan of indie##1
7. the fan of indie is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the fan of country is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta         | coffee  | iced-tea     | water         |
| Music-Genre        | country | ambient | indie | funk         |
| Birthday      | september         | october  | november   | june |

