.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, turquise, purple, pink
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, sports, satire, family
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, lizard, mouse
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
 2. the person watching romance movies is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes ivory##2
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is the person who likes purple##1
 7. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes ivory is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching sports movies is between the person who likes pink and the person who likes purple##2
10. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | ivory  | purple    | turquise | pink    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | satire | sports  | family |
| Pet           | lizard   | mouse    | dog        | horse   |

