.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
4 different games are played: canasta, go, whist, monopoly
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bolivar, oliveros, bongani
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
4. the person playing go is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
6. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person playing go##1
7. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person playing go##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| Game           | monopoly | go | canasta   | whist |
| Cigar   | bolivar         | swisher     | bongani     | oliveros |

