.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cherry, lime, peach
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, scientist, coach, doctor
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, domino, poker
1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the scientist##1
5. the person playing backgammon is between the doctor and the person playing poker##2
6. the coach is in an even position##4
7. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lime    | cherry  | peach  | avocado |
| Job   | doctor | scientist | bartender | coach |
| Game   | domino    | backgammon     | poker    | monopoly |

