.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, fuchsia, lilac, chestnut
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, electrician, accountant, mechanic
1. the electrician is between the person who likes lilac and the argentine##2
2. the person who likes brown is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the accountant##3
4. the mechanic is on the left of the australian##1
5. the mechanic is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the accountant##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person who likes brown##1
9. the turkish is between the accountant and the videographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Color      | brown | lilac      | fuchsia  | chestnut    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Job           | mechanic      | accountant       | electrician   | videographer      |

