.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, scientific, drama
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, police-officer, electrician, designer
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the fisherman##2
3. the police-officer is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
5. the fisherman is on the right of the electrician##1
6. the person watching drama movies is between the fisherman and the person watching family movies##2
7. the police-officer is on the far right##1
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an even position##4
9. the fisherman is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving  |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | martial-arts       | drama | family |
| Job         | electrician   | fisherman      | designer | police-officer       |

