3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's sport is swimming##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
