.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, gospel, folk, classical
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, march, october
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, snowmobile
1. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
5. the fan of gospel is between the person driving the bike and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre    | folk    | gospel     | salsa    | classical        |
| Birthday       | march   | may | april | october |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car      | bike    | airplane   |

