4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat, guinea-pig, cat
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, iced-tea, mirinda
1. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking cola and the person eating tomato##2
3. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating tomato is the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | tomato  | cabbage   | lemon    |
| Pet   | chinchilla  | guinea-pig     | cat | rat |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | mirinda | milk | cola   |

