.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, poppy, orchid, iris
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, hiking, reading
4 different games are played: whist, monopoly, mah-jongg, poker
1. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
5. the person who growspoppy is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
8. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Flower    | orchid    | poppy    | azalea  | iris |
| Hobby   | reading | board-games | baking | hiking      |
| Game     | monopoly   | whist        | poker   | mah-jongg       |

 